00025 //---------------------------------------------------------
00026 //   font
00027 //    Create symbol font
00028 //---------------------------------------------------------
00029 
00030 QFont Sym::font() const
00031       {
00032       TextStyle* s = &textStyles[textStyle];
00033       QFont f(s->family);
00034       f.setStyleStrategy(QFont::PreferMatch);
00035       f.setPixelSize(lrint(20.0 / 5.0 * _spatium));
00036       return f;
00037       }
00038 
00039 //---------------------------------------------------------
00040 //   bbox
00041 //---------------------------------------------------------
00042 
00043 QRectF Sym::bbox() const
00044       {
00045       QFontMetricsF fm(font());
00046       return QRectF(fm.boundingRect(_code));
00047       }
00048 
00049 //---------------------------------------------------------
00050 //   width
00051 //---------------------------------------------------------
00052 
00053 double Sym::width() const
00054       {
00055       return bbox().width();
00056       }
00057 
00058 //---------------------------------------------------------
00059 //   height
00060 //---------------------------------------------------------
00061 
00062 double Sym::height() const
00063       {
00064       return bbox().height();
00065       }
00066 
00067 //---------------------------------------------------------
00068 //   baseline
00069 //---------------------------------------------------------
00070 
00071 double Sym::baseline() const
00072       {
00073       QFont f = font();
00074       QFontMetricsF fm(f);
00075       return fm.height();;
00076       }

00078 //---------------------------------------------------------
00079 //   draw
00080 //---------------------------------------------------------
00081 
00082 void Sym::draw(Painter& painter, qreal x, qreal y) const
00083       {
00084       painter.setFont(font());
00085       painter.drawText(QPointF(x, y), QString(QChar(_code)));
00086       }
